Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura's Diabound attacked while hiding within the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was able to defeat Osiris the Heaven Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after we gave him strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my other self managed to Summon Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura was beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or so we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, time began flowing backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura was revived and my other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Pharaoh is Still Alive"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter {\i1}who{\i0} it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take her out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman... Show me the power of your {\i1}Ka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Akhenaden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you waiting for?\N Call out your {\i0}Ka{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't, you'll....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even on the verge of death, she's still resisting...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there really a {\i0}Ka{\i1}\N in this woman's body...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What.... is this light...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman! Call out your {\i1}Ka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to die if you keep this up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you have a {\i0}Ka{\i1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.... what do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman... What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara, don't leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never woulda guessed a {\i1}priest{\i0} would be joining us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got grudges worth years of suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it about time you pay for it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman can't even call out a {\i1}Ka{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's two-on-one, we hold the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scum! Don't you dare harm Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move a muscle, geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're as good as goners!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who the hell cares if we drag one little "Holy Priest" down with us to Hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. Then give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?!\N - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aura Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved thanks to this guy, Mister "Holy Priest"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as you can see, {\i1}your Ka{\i0} wound up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet a Holy Priest's gotta \Nbe {\i1}scrumptious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gobble 'im up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SETO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's.... the white dragon from that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's up with that dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That white dragon is the {\i1}Ka{\i0}\N this woman gave birth to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...! KILL THEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the attack of a God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her rest in her room for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.... that white dragon's power may exceed that of Bakura's Diabound...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Even the Three Illusionary Beast Gods of the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}Ka{\i0} is different from any other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is most likely that\N the White Dragon is a {\i1}Ba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto! You must steal \Nthe {\i1}Ka{\i0} from that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if her {\i1}Ka{\i0} really\N is connected to her {\i1}Ba{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stealing the White Dragon\Nmeans the {\i1}death{\i0} of that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hesitating!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill that woman and extract the White Dragon from within her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will wield a {\i1}God!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only at that moment will the throne accept you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the new Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are still yet to locate the missing Pharaoh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not where the Pharaoh is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the current Pharaoh does not return, who will inherit his position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand, Seto?! It's {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden! The Pharaoh is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way someone as I, who does not wield a God, could ever replace him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land needs the Pharaoh's authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do right now\N is look for the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is enough for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time will come sooner or later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where you come to\N learn your destiny, my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I got my hands on the Millennium Puzzle this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenaden has already\N become my game piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remains are the remaining priests and the other small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can all just sit quietly\N and await your deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ecstatic, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all the Millennium Items are gathered, the Door of the Underworld will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my original body, the Great Wicked God Zorc, will revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that moment comes, the Eighth Key will appear as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I know its location,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to break the seal and revive Zorc in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so irritated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that {\i1}hurts{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you not happy with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eighth Key...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the Eighth Key the key that sealed Zorc away 3,000 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment the seal on Zorc is broken and he emerges back into this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Pharaoh was just killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game still continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that must mean the king left a clue behind in his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3,000 years ago, the Pharaoh used the Eighth Key to seal everything inside of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, he wouldn't want anyone to find the Eighth Key ever again....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was me, what would I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.... I'd erase all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it... I know what it is now... the Eighth Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry! Now I'm thirsty~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so damn heavy Bobasa! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water, water~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oi, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nile river?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}huge{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my other self?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cliff lead to the river....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so if we follow the Nile, we might find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water, WATER~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, Bobasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly... Lightly... Lightly~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Progress, progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Move, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed again~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try, I just can't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Black Magician Girl, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looks just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the prince here of all places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you dressed in this weird outfit and with these weird people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weird people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible this girl can see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be Bobasa's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bo" in Bobasa~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stands for the "Bo" in "Bobbing Glutton~"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Bobasa! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Yugi's cape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa wanted to eat fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a {\i1}fish!{\i0} It's a {\i1}cape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the cape's not edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean {\i1}that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cape was floating along the river, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Yugi's around here somewhere...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so... But he may have been washed away by the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things more complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self must be close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! That's Prince's cape, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Prince?\N - Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, that's not right.... I meant Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You....! You know my other self?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really not Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we.... We're the Pharaoh's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, since you know Yugi...\N No, the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know, but he's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They followed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are the one who killed Master, Bakura's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys really Prince's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're {\i1}my{\i0} friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go look for Prince while we have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shada, we searched all over the surrounding area,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we haven't found the Pharaoh anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the search team for Bakura reported yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found Bakura's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is.... Spiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis.... You must find the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Millennium Puzzle has been stolen by Bakura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cut the bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Holy Pharaoh", my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akhenamkhanen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the {\i0}last{\i1} person I'd call that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Didn't he create the Millennium Items you're all wearing to gain {\i0}evil power!?{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that the holders of the Millennium Items gain great powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But those items also respond to the darkness in the holders' heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and drags them into\N the World of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quite the problem-makers they can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, why did you create the Millennium Items?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Didn't you know these items would bring nothing but pain and misfortune to the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there no way you can answer me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have no memories of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The prince is so healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your heir as Pharaoh has finally been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heir as Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is the passion I felt as he comforted me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...! I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the heir to the throne, you must not say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes... Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand...! I feel it! Your voice is shaking, Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...! I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Souls of our great ancestors....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have committed an unforgivable sin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This thousand-year sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No....! Please put the blame of the creation of seven the Millennium Items on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you! I pray that my son does not inherit my sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please let me take all the suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...? Are you crying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I.... I will take all the consequences on my shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know how much father loved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, the Great Evil God Zorc is about to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only {\i1}you{\i0} can defeat Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorc?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former king Akhenamkhanen is also watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're studying magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always used to hold my master back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in our world, there's\N this thing called a card game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this card character\N girl who looks just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's called Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very powerful girl spellcaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work hard, you can be just as strong as Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has a cool ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Bo" in Bobasa~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Bobasa, don't just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Thank God...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PRINCE~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PRINCE~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we believed you were alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until we saw it, we were really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bakura has stolen\Nyour Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't regained your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priest Shada knows where Bakura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yugi is heading\Nfor the Kul Elna village....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! We don't know what traps are waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Village of Dead Spirits"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
